Service Staff signs in.
Service Staff clicks on “Time-Off” button.
System displays a request form.
Service Staff selects the type of leave (i.e.: vacation, sick leave), specifies the dates 
Service Staff submits the form.
System sends a notification to the manager.
Manager reviews the form.
System sends a notification to the staff.

Alternate/Exceptional Flows:
9a. If the manager approves the request, the system updates the schedule to reflect the time off and sends a confirmation to the staff.
9b. If the manager denies the request, the system sends a rejection notification to the staff
